step.reason:
\text{The terms are decreasing and hence }d\lt 0\newline
\text{And more generally, }d = a_{n+1} - a_n \newline
\text{where } a_{n+1} = \text{(n+1)-th term and }a_n = \text{n-th term}

step.tex:
a_n\lt 0\implies 125-4n\lt 0
ewline \implies 4n\gt 125\implies n\gt 31.25
ewline 	ext{But as }n	ext{ is an integer, the smallest }n\gt 31.25	ext{ is } n=32
ewline 	ext{Which means, after 31 terms, the first negative}
ewline 	ext{term will appear}

